        <div class="text_pref_1">
            <p>Counter-Strike Global Offensive or CSGO for short, is a fast paced team based fps, in which, in ranked matches, two teams of five go against each other under the teams of counter terrorists and terrorists. The community is <b>EXTREMELY</b> toxic in most cases so be prepared for harassment if your new to the game, and/or you don't perform at your best. Other than the community the game is all around fun to play. It is both hard to play and hard to master, so be ready to grind if you want to get a high rank. A warning for any who play this game, do <b>NOT</b> get caught up into the world of skins, it will cost you your life and family.</p>
            <br />
            <p>>>>....HAVE FUN</p>
