    <div class="pref_2_text">
        <p>Player Unkowns Battlegrounds or more commonly known as PUBG is a free roaming 100 player battle royale, in which the players drop from a cargo plane that flies over the entirety of the map, and players must scavenge for loot and head to the play area, which will be marked by a white cricle. This game is fun to play alone, but I find that the most entertainment can be taken from his game when played with friends. PUBG has recently started to go downhill with recent skin additions and the such, starting to turn into a CSGO copy, however, the updates for weapons and their balancing makes it still playable and enjoyable.</p>
        <br /> 
        <p>>>>....GOOD LUCK</p>
