    <div class="pref_3_text">
        <p>Skyrim is agurably one of the best open world games that has ever come out. It has an extremely long playtime, hundreds of side quests, multiple different skills to master, and an economic system that can be tracked (for the most part). Skyrim is a medieval and magic based rpg that can be played in both first or third person. This game will make you lose track of your time, your kids, and your job. It is both fun to play, and fun to mod, as there is a large community that provides a workshop full of different mods for you to explore. This game is best purchased off steam, and not the newly updated one, but the original, as the new version of Skyrim has issues that affect gameplay.</p>
        <br />
        <p>>>>....KEEP YOUR EYE ON THE TIME</p>
